               <msContents>
                  <summary>Gospel of John, ወንጌል፡ ዘዮሐንስ፡; Table Prayer, “We beseech you,” ሰአልናከ፡</summary>
                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i1">
                    <locus from="1r" to="47r" facs="003">Fols 1r–47r</locus>
                    <textLang mainLang="gez">Gǝ‘ǝz</textLang>
                    <title type="complete" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT1693John">Gospel of John</title>
                    <note>at <locus target="#46v #47r" facs="049">fols. 46v, 47r</locus>‎</note>
                    <explicit xml:lang="gez">መልዓ፡ ጽሕፈተ፡ ብስራቱ፡ ለዮሐንስ፡ ሐዋርያ፡ ዘጸሐፎ፡ በልሳን፡ ዮናናዊ፡ ለሰብአ፡ ኤፌሶን፡ እምድኅረ፡ ዕርገቱ፡ ለእግዚአነ፡ በሥጋ፡ ውስተ፡ ሰማይ፡ <gap reason="omitted"/></explicit>
                  </msItem>
                </msContents>
